---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Components
description: Generated component reference index for the Aihio design system.
---
<section class="docs-page-intro">
  <div class="docs-eyebrow">
    <aihio-badge>Component inventory</aihio-badge>
    <aihio-badge variant="outline">{{ docs.componentCount }} components</aihio-badge>
  </div>
  <h1>Generated Component Index</h1>
  <p>
    Each card here is backed by the emitted schema in <code>dist/schema.json</code>. Phase 1 ships the overview and inventory;
    detail pages land in the next commit.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <aihio-alert>
    <div slot="title">Schema-backed reference</div>
    <div slot="description">Counts, intents, and versions below are generated, not maintained by hand.</div>
  </aihio-alert>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="docs-component-grid">
    {% for component in docs.components %}
      {% include "partials/component-card.njk" %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
